HOW TO INSTALL:

1. EXTRACT BOTH CD1 and CD2 to same folder (or mount 'em).

2. Run Setup.exe

3. Copy files from Patch 1.1 and NoCD 1.1 into the Flatout Folder (over-writing old exe twice)

4. Run game.  It should work fine without the CD.

If it's not too much trouble, the game is worth every bit of the $30.
